{"tid":2052073,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"三代火影同初代火影邊個勁啲？","createTime":"2020-06-05T08:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T15:03:37.000Z","uid":82404,"like":39,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"960c5ca8e5ec10f19c68e0b6abd05fe490b0b902","tid":2052073,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:46:37.000Z","msg":"兩個都比人叫做忍者之神，但三代多兩個朵叫做歷代最強火影同忍術教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講實力，真數千手係勁，但三代都有手裏劍影分身，仲可以將五遁溝埋落手裏劍，諗起都覺得勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上馬騮最叻就係爬樹，三代隻猿魔完美counter初代，認真打應該55波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n智力更加唔駛講，三代忍術讀到上phd，初代書都未撚讀過...<br />\n仲維穩維到全村都唔覺有問題(滅宇智波，恰鳩鳴仔)，然後乜都屈曬落團藏到，手段高超<br />\n<br />\n講戰績，三代單挑大蛇丸+1+2代。你可能話12代唔係最佳狀態，但三代都唔係全盛期。同埋贏就贏，輸就輸，冇得瀨<br />\n<br />\n結論：三代又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44cfda2aca0353653a6eee071a0fe7dbdfce096","tid":2052073,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:47:58.000Z","msg":"淨係影分身瓦片手裡劍已經屈曬"},{"pid":"dae3d3f22e5b4761af2f7a07779d99ee4ee60949","tid":2052073,"uid":1837,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:49:00.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野<br />\n三代贏到班？"},{"pid":"88ee90984cb53aed17be95667526b46c994782ba","tid":2052073,"uid":41292,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:49:44.000Z","msg":"靠影分身做到火影嘅人<br />\n<br />\n實力係無底洞黎"},{"pid":"75fe7341af43e8310956105b04d128a44c9de8aa","tid":2052073,"uid":146185,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"馬騮counter 樹呢個論點駁唔到<br />\n三代完勝"},{"pid":"25fef6983bedb8a0d1df2218daea0cf916f91774","tid":2052073,"uid":122134,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">加上馬騮最叻就係爬樹</span><br />\n<br />\n秒"},{"pid":"0bc159647eefecc31365fc1d1b053d0cbfd810f1